fields.calculatedFormula:
IF(
                ISBLANK(vlocity_cmt__RequestedCompletionDate__c) || ISNULL(vlocity_cmt__RequestedCompletionDate__c) || ISBLANK(vlocity_cmt__DueDate__c) || ISNULL(vlocity_cmt__DueDate__c),
                    'Green',
                    IF(
                        vlocity_cmt__DueDate__c >= vlocity_cmt__RequestedCompletionDate__c,
                            'Red',
                            IF(
                                vlocity_cmt__JeopardySafetyInterval__c <= 0,
                                'Green',
                                CASE(vlocity_cmt__JeopardySafetyIntervalUnit__c,
                                    'Seconds', IF(vlocity_cmt__DueDate__c + (vlocity_cmt__JeopardySafetyInterval__c/(24*60*60)) <= vlocity_cmt__RequestedCompletionDate__c, 'Green', 'Yellow'),
                                    'Calendar Hours', IF(vlocity_cmt__DueDate__c + (vlocity_cmt__JeopardySafetyInterval__c/24) <= vlocity_cmt__RequestedCompletionDate__c, 'Green', 'Yellow'),
                                    'Calendar Days', IF(vlocity_cmt__DueDate__c + vlocity_cmt__JeopardySafetyInterval__c <= vlocity_cmt__RequestedCompletionDate__c, 'Green', 'Yellow'),
                                    /* TODO: Gap - business intervals doesn't support business calendar */
                                    'Business Hours', IF(vlocity_cmt__DueDate__c + (vlocity_cmt__JeopardySafetyInterval__c/24) <= vlocity_cmt__RequestedCompletionDate__c, 'Green', 'Yellow'),
                                    'Business Days', IF(vlocity_cmt__DueDate__c + vlocity_cmt__JeopardySafetyInterval__c <= vlocity_cmt__RequestedCompletionDate__c, 'Green', 'Yellow'),
                                'Green')
                            )
                    )
            )
fields.label: Jeopardy Status
fields.name: vlocity_cmt__JeopardyStatus__c
